enchantments.name: Fire Protection
enchantments.description: Reduces fire damage and burn time. Mutually exclusive with other protections.

enchantments.name: Feather Falling
enchantments.description: Reduces fall damage

enchantments.name: Blast Protection
enchantments.description: Reduces explosion damage and knockback.

enchantments.name: Projectile Protection
enchantments.description: Reduces damage from projectiles.

enchantments.name: Respiration
enchantments.description: Increases underwater breathing time.

enchantments.name: Aqua Affinity
enchantments.description: Increases underwater mining speed.

enchantments.name: Thorns
enchantments.description: Taking damage causes the attacker to also take damage.

enchantments.name: Depth Strider
enchantments.description: Increases underwater movement speed.

enchantments.name: Frost Walker
enchantments.description: Allows the player to walk on water by freezing the water under their feet.

enchantments.name: Curse of Binding
enchantments.description: Prevents the item from being removed from the player's inventory.

enchantments.name: Soul Speed
enchantments.description: Increases movement speed on soul sand and soul soil.

enchantments.name: Swift Sneak
enchantments.description: Increases sneaking speed.

enchantments.name: Sharpness
enchantments.description: Increases melee damage.

enchantments.name: Smite
enchantments.description: Increases melee damage against undead mobs.

enchantments.name: Bane of arthropods
enchantments.description: Increases damage and applies Slowness IV to arthropod mobs (spiders, cave spiders, silverfish, endermites and bees).

enchantments.name: Knockback
enchantments.description: Increases knockback.

enchantments.name: Fire aspect
enchantments.description: Sets the target on fire

enchantments.name: Looting
enchantments.description: Increases the chance of getting extra loot from mobs.

enchantments.name: Sweeping Edge
enchantments.description: Deals damage to nearby mobs when attacking.

enchantments.name: Unbreaking
enchantments.description: Increases durability and reduce durability damage

enchantments.name: Power
enchantments.description: Increases arrow damage.

enchantments.name: Punch
enchantments.description: Increases arrows knockback.

enchantments.name: Flame
enchantments.description: Arrows set targets on fire.

enchantments.name: Infinity
enchantments.description: Arrows are not consumed when shot.

enchantments.name: Loyalty
enchantments.description: Returns the trident to the player when thrown.

enchantments.name: Impaling
enchantments.description: Increases damage against aquatic mobs. In Bedrock Edition, increases damage against mobs in water or rain.

enchantments.name: Riptide
enchantments.description: Trident launches player with itself when thrown while in water or rain.

enchantments.name: Chanelling
enchantments.description: During thunderstorms, tridents can strike enemies with a lightning bolt.

enchantments.name: Multishot
enchantments.description: Shoots 3 arrows at once.

enchantments.name: Quick Charge
enchantments.description: Increases the speed at which the crossbow is reloaded.

enchantments.name: Piercing
enchantments.description: Arrows pierce entities, allowing for arrows to pierce through stacks of mobs.

enchantments.name: Mending
enchantments.description: Repairs the item when the player collects experience.

enchantments.name: Curse of Vanishing
enchantments.description: The item will disappear when dropped or when the player dies.

enchantments.name: Efficiency
enchantments.description: Increases the speed at which blocks are mined.

enchantments.name: Silk Touch
enchantments.description: Mined blocks drop themselves.

enchantments.name: Fortune
enchantments.description: Increases the amount of items dropped from blocks.

enchantments.name: Luck of the sea
enchantments.description: Increases rate of good loot (enchanting books, etc.).

enchantments.name: Lure
enchantments.description: Increases the rate at which fish are caught.
